rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0001
rows.name:
Before we set out from Yanchik
Harbor, we should really try and fix
that ether miasma.

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0002
rows.name: Kasumi. This'll be one for you.

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0003
rows.name: Got it! Leave it to me!

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0004
rows.name:
Ugh, why?
You don't have to do this, you know.

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0005
rows.name:
Come now, Hikari. We can't just
leave the stuff hanging around for some
unwary traveler to walk right into.

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0007
rows.name:
Kasumi is gonna use her ether powers,
right? Eh, maybe I'll tag along for a
while.

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0008
rows.name: Haha! I knew you'd come round.
